---
title: Integrations
layout: base.njk
---

<div class="max-w-4xl">
  <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl mb-2">Integrations</h1>
  <p class="text-fg-3 text-sm mb-10">Lead paragraph with a three-column icon grid. Each tile has a logo and label.</p>

  <div class="rounded-lg border border-line bg-surface-1 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="px-6 md:px-10 py-16 md:py-24">
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-fg-3 leading-snug tracking-tight max-w-2xl"><span class="text-fg-1">Integrations.</span> Connect to the tools your team already uses. Interloom reads, writes, and syncs data across your stack so workflows stay grounded in live systems.</p>

      <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        {% for name in ["SharePoint", "Salesforce", "SAP", "Microsoft Teams", "Confluence", "Google Workspace", "ServiceNow", "Jira Service Management", "Slack"] %}
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-lg border border-line bg-surface-2 px-4 py-4">
          <div class="h-8 w-8 shrink-0 rounded bg-surface-3 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-fg-4 text-[10px] font-mono">{{ name[0] }}</span>
          </div>
          <span class="text-fg-2 text-sm font-medium">{{ name }}</span>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
